OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe NHS in England will roll out
OL,8,F'Martha's Rule' from April to give
OL,9,Fpatients and families access to a
OL,10,Frapid review if they are worried about
OL,11,Fa condition getting worse.
OL,13,FThe escalation process, which
OL,14,Fformalises access to a critical care
OL,15,Fteam for a second opinion, will be
OL,16,Favailable 24/7 and will be advertised
OL,17,Fthroughout hospitals.
