OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FUnder the move, an urgent clinical
OL,8,Freview would be carried out by a
OL,9,Fdifferent team in the hospital if a
OL,10,Fpatient's condition is rapidly
OL,11,Fworsening and they or their family
OL,12,Ffeels they are not getting the care
OL,13,Fneeded.
OL,15,FAt least 100 NHS trusts are expected
OL,16,Fto bring in the rule, with the
OL,17,Fprogramme evaluated throughout this
OL,18,Fyear and next.
