OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe plan is to then extend Martha's
OL,8,FRule to all acute hospitals, subject
OL,9,Fto Government funding.
OL,11,FThe move follows the death of 13-year-
OL,12,Fold Martha Mills in 2021. She
OL,13,Fdeveloped sepsis while under the care
OL,14,Fof King's College Hospital NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust in south London.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/16
