OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FA coroner ruled she would most likely
OL,8,Fhave survived if doctors had
OL,9,Fidentified the warning signs of her
OL,10,Frapidly deteriorating condition and
OL,11,Ftransferred her to intensive care
OL,12,Fearlier.
OL,14,FMartha's parents, Merope Mills, an
OL,15,Feditor at the Guardian, and her
OL,16,Fhusband Paul Laity, raised concerns
OL,17,Fabout Martha's health a number of
OL,18,Ftimes but these were brushed aside.
