OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe pair have since campaigned for
OL,8,FMartha's Rule to be introduced to give
OL,9,Ffamilies more say.
OL,11,FThey said in a statement: "We are
OL,12,Fpleased that the implementation of
OL,13,FMartha's Rule will begin in April.
OL,15,F"We want it to be in place as quickly
OL,16,Fand as widely as possible, to prevent
OL,17,Fwhat happened to our daughter from
OL,18,Fhappening to other patients in
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,26,@sD@[OUwD@AOU
