OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"We believe Martha's Rule will save
OL,8,Flives. In cases of deterioration,
OL,9,Ffamilies and carers by the bedside can
OL,10,Fbe aware of changes busy clinicians
OL,11,Fcan't; their knowledge should be
OL,12,Frecognised as a resource.
OL,14,F"We also look to Martha's Rule to
OL,15,Falter medical culture: to give
OL,16,Fpatients a little more power, to
OL,17,Fencourage listening on the part of
OL,18,Fmedical professionals, and to
OL,19,Fnormalise the idea that even the
OL,20,Fgrandest of doctors should welcome
OL,21,Fbeing challenged.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
