OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"We call on all NHS clinicians to back
OL,8,Fthe initiative: we know that the large
OL,9,Fmajority do listen, are open with
OL,10,Fpatients and never complacent ` but
OL,11,FMartha's doctors worked in a different
OL,12,Fculture, so some situations need to
OL,13,Fchange.
OL,15,F"Our daughter was quite something: fun
OL,16,Fand determined, with a vast appetite
OL,17,Ffor life and so many plans and
OL,18,Fambitions ` we'll never know what she
OL,19,Fwould have achieved with all her
OL,20,Ftalents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
