OL,7,FShe also developed a rash and her
OL,8,Fmother voiced concerns to staff that
OL,9,FMartha would go into septic shock over
OL,10,Fa bank holiday weekend.
OL,12,FOne of the trust's own intensive care
OL,13,Fdoctors told the inquest into Martha's
OL,14,Fdeath he would "100%" have admitted
OL,15,Fher if he had seen her.
OL,17,FRegarding the introduction of Martha's
OL,18,FRule, NHS chief executive Amanda
OL,19,FPritchard said it had the potential to
OL,20,F"save many lives in the future".
