OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FShe said: "Hearing about the
OL,8,Fheartbreaking loss of Martha and the
OL,9,Fexperiences of her family has had a
OL,10,Fmajor impact for people right across
OL,11,Fthe country, with parents, patients
OL,12,Fand NHS staff welcoming her parents'
OL,13,Fcall for a simple process to escalate
OL,14,Fconcerns when they can see a loved
OL,15,Fone's condition worsening.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
