OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"NHS teams have been piloting ways to
OL,8,Fbetter identify and respond in these
OL,9,Fcases over the last year, and the roll-
OL,10,Fout of a national programme to give
OL,11,Fpatients and families 24/7 access to a
OL,12,Frapid clinical review will now help
OL,13,Fensure that those experiencing acute
OL,14,Fdeterioration can be identified and
OL,15,Ftreated much more quickly.
OL,17,F"I know I speak on behalf of all NHS
OL,18,Fstaff when I thank Merope and Paul for
OL,19,Ftheir extraordinary campaigning and
OL,20,Fcollaboration on this hugely important
OL,21,Fissue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/16
