OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"While the need for escalation will
OL,8,Fhopefully only be needed in a small
OL,9,Fnumber of cases, I have no doubt that
OL,10,Fthe introduction of Martha's Rule has
OL,11,Fthe potential to save many lives in
OL,12,Fthe future."
OL,14,FNHS teams will also look at ways ways
OL,15,Fto roll out an adapted Martha's Rule
OL,16,Fmodel in community and mental health
OL,17,Fhospitals.
OL,19,FRory Deighton, director of the NHS
OL,20,FConfederation's acute network,
OL,21,Fwelcomed the move.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]
