OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FHe said: "Questions remain about what
OL,8,Fresources hospitals and other
OL,9,Fproviders will be given to deliver the
OL,10,Fnew scheme.
OL,12,F"Introducing a 24/7 clinical review
OL,13,Fprocess will have implementation costs
OL,14,Fand leaders will be concerned if they
OL,15,Fare just being expected to provide the
OL,16,Fadditional service without any extra
OL,17,Fresources.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOU
