OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"But this rollout is part of an
OL,8,Fimportant shift where the NHS is
OL,9,Flooking to change the relationship
OL,10,Fbetween the NHS, clinicians, patients
OL,11,Fand their families.
OL,13,F"The future model of care is one where
OL,14,Fpatients and their families are active
OL,15,Fpartners in healthy communities, not
OL,16,Fjust consumers of NHS services."
OL,18,FHealth Secretary Victoria Atkins said:
OL,19,F"Martha's death was a terrible
OL,20,Ftragedy, and I pay tribute to her
OL,21,Fparents Merope and Paul.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@`O]{D@AOU
