OL,3,CNHS to roll out 'Martha's Rule' from
OL,4,CApril in bid to help patients and
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"Martha's Rule will provide a major
OL,8,Fboost to patient safety by putting in
OL,9,Fplace a system that can be triggered
OL,10,Fby patients, or by their family and
OL,11,Ffriends, when they are worried that
OL,12,Ftheir condition is worsening. This
OL,13,Fwill give vital reassurance that the
OL,14,Fbest care possible is being given.
OL,16,F"The introduction of Martha's Rule
OL,17,Ffrom April will put families at the
OL,18,Fheart of the patient's own care,
OL,19,Frecognising the critical role they
OL,20,Fhave in the treatment of loved ones."
